<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><placeName>Burnbank<add place="marginleft">194</add>
<lb/>Hamilton</placeName> 
<lb/><date when="1857-09-21">Monday 21st
<lb/>[Sept. 1857]</date></dateline><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear Friend,</salute></opener><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/><p>I got your
<lb/>note a minute
<lb/>ago just when
<lb/>on the point of 
<lb/>startng for
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="city">Edinburgh</settlement></placeName> on
<lb/>Thursday we are
<lb/>at <placeName><settlement type="city">Dundee</settlement></placeName>

	<pb facs="liv_001098_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>Saturday <unclear cert="low">Kendal</unclear> on 
<lb/>our way to 
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="city">Liverpool</settlement></placeName> v <placeName><settlement type="city">Leeds</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>if my mother's 
<lb/>illness does not
<lb/>become serious
<lb/>I asked every
<lb/>body for the <!-- unable to read word -->
<lb/>the <unclear cert="low">Dresbytery</unclear>
<lb/>sir <persName>James Anderson</persName>
<lb/>but no doctor
<lb/>to be seen <!-- unclear character -->now

	<pb facs="liv_001098_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>I fear I am off
<lb/>before seeeing you 
<lb/><unclear cert="low">Liorioying</unclear> very
<lb/>disagreeable I assure
<lb/>you <!-- unclear character --> very glad
<lb/>I shall be to bid
<lb/>adeu to it for
<lb/>ever <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> L.</persName>
<lb/>follows me to - 
<lb/>morrow - part
<lb/>with the <term type="nationality">Canadian</term>
<lb/>brother today - he 
<lb/><unclear cert="low">grees</unclear> to <placeName><settlement type="city">Liverpool</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>to sail thence

	<pb facs="liv_001098_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> L.</persName> joins in
<lb/>kindest salutations
<lb/>to yourself and
<lb/>to <!-- unclear word -->
</p>

<!-- If there is a letter or similar with a closer with content such as salute or signed -->
